        "TileImage": "$($repository 22d36967-af1e-4329-9921-03b851e4018c).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. Our client, a leader of Crystal Dawn, has ordered a contract on five key figures of the Burj Al-Ghazali during its grand opening. It appears that Sheikh Omar Al-Ghazali promised them a political stranglehold in the UAE in exchange for the building&apos;s funds, but betrayed the organization, giving them nothing. The client has requested this contract be done as quickly and as silently as possible. Luckily, 47, quick and silent is your forte. I will leave you to prepare.",
